item.title: CVE-2020-1832|2024-08-04T06:46:30.938Z -- huawei -- e6878-370
item.description: E6878-370 products with versions of 10.0.3.1(H557SP27C233) and 10.0.3.1(H563SP1C00) have a stack buffer overflow vulnerability. The program copies an input buffer to an output buffer without verification. An attacker in the adjacent network could send a crafted message, successful exploit could lead to stack buffer overflow which may cause malicious code execution.
